=head1 DESCRIPTION

The structure containing the size and type of the network attached
storage (NAS_1) file system volume.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Size => Int

The size of the network attached storage. For storage type C<SSD_1000>
and C<SSD_250> you can select the minimum size as 1200 GB or increments
of 2400 GB. For storage type C<HDD_12> you can select the minimum size
as 6000 GB or increments of 6000 GB.


=head2 Type => Str

The type of the network attached storage.



